# API sample logger output (backend/src/utils/apiSamples.ts) - raw debug
# dumps of real API responses, several hundred KB per file, meant for
# local reference during development only. One of these (squad/*.json
# for 7 countries) was accidentally committed at ~7.3MB total in commit
